Setting up NGINX
****************

This web server will be serving static content: the converted data (octree LAZ by the POtree converter)

Modify configuration file in /etc/nginx/nginx.conf

1 - Comment lines:
#include /etc/nginx/conf.d/*.conf;
#include /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/*;

2 - Add server description:
        server {
            listen 80;
            location / {
                root /home/vadata/DATA/RAW/PC/BACKGROUND/DRIVE_1_V3;
            }
        }